text: The Samsung Galaxy J7 Prime is a mobile phone sold by Samsung. It was first released on September 19, 2016. It is a part of the Samsung Galaxy J7 line. It has a 5.5 inch display size, 8MP front camera, 13MP rear camera, 3300mAh battery capacity and 1080P FHD 30fps video recording rear camera. == References == Category:Samsung Galaxy Category:Mobile phones introduced in 2016
title: Samsung Galaxy J7 Prime
